WEBVTT

01:35.700 --> 01:39.980
[Veil of Shadows]

01:39.980 --> 01:42.980
[Episode 4]

01:58.700 --> 01:59.770
No need to fight.

02:01.500 --> 02:02.810
Because we got tricked too.

02:46.200 --> 02:46.850
No problem.

02:48.080 --> 02:48.930
One more.

03:00.370 --> 03:00.980
Thank you.

03:01.450 --> 03:02.140
You're welcome.

03:07.450 --> 03:08.850
What that disciple at Weimiao Pavilion said

03:08.850 --> 03:10.350
was false.

03:10.920 --> 03:12.580
She was deceived by Xiaowei too.

03:14.370 --> 03:15.590
You found the talisman

03:15.590 --> 03:16.850
in Li Mao's hand, didn't you?

03:18.950 --> 03:19.560
That's right.

03:21.370 --> 03:23.430
If it were really as that disciple said,

03:23.950 --> 03:25.980
and his wife, who asked for the talisman, had torn it up,

03:26.830 --> 03:27.560
how could

03:28.200 --> 03:29.520
the talisman have ended up in Li Mao's hand?

03:33.370 --> 03:35.350
Before Wangyan and I came to the Wei mansion,

03:35.660 --> 03:37.790
we'd already investigated the three victims.

03:38.450 --> 03:40.020
When they died,

03:40.620 --> 03:42.340
they were all clutching a love talisman.

03:43.790 --> 03:44.520
So the truth is

03:44.940 --> 03:46.980
that the one under the spell will suffer the blowback

03:47.250 --> 03:48.480
only if they tear the talisman up themselves?

03:48.870 --> 03:50.350
Wei Qing's death

03:50.450 --> 03:51.680
proves that too.

03:53.000 --> 03:53.810
Which means

03:54.500 --> 03:56.430
Li Mao died because he tore up the talisman himself.

04:02.250 --> 04:04.730
How could you use something this filthy on me?

04:05.570 --> 04:06.730
How could you?

04:10.250 --> 04:11.480
Once someone is targeted by a love talisman,

04:11.870 --> 04:13.520
their heart will be

04:13.540 --> 04:15.430
slowly eroded by the Fox-Allure Spell within it.

04:16.290 --> 04:17.930
And once the talisman is destroyed,

04:18.370 --> 04:19.310
the person under the spell

04:19.790 --> 04:21.850
will die from unbearable heartache.

04:22.200 --> 04:23.850
Only Xiaowei knew the truth,

04:25.790 --> 04:28.270
so she must've been the one who switched the talismans.

04:28.660 --> 04:30.100
She wanted Wei Qing dead.

04:31.750 --> 04:33.520
With everyone who wanted to catch Xiaowei gathering in the Wei mansion,

04:34.120 --> 04:35.480
the protective barrier you set up,

04:35.950 --> 04:37.600
and the Ice Curse in play,

04:38.040 --> 04:39.600
she didn't dare use demon magic recklessly.

04:41.200 --> 04:42.850
But she still wanted Wei Qing dead,

04:43.660 --> 04:45.270
so she had to leverage the blowback

04:45.370 --> 04:46.270
of the Fox-Allure Spell.

04:47.080 --> 04:48.850
The Ice Curse's true name

04:49.410 --> 04:50.230
is the Never-Ending Curse.

04:50.660 --> 04:52.460
Anyone who betrays the Formless Moon Sect

04:52.500 --> 04:53.810
will be hunted

04:53.870 --> 04:55.630
by this curse for all eternity.

04:56.080 --> 04:56.770
The Never-Ending Curse?

04:59.200 --> 05:00.270
Didn't you read widely

05:00.290 --> 05:01.480
back at the Shilin Sect?

05:02.620 --> 05:03.350
Haven't you read about it?

05:04.790 --> 05:06.640
I can be a bit playful sometimes.

05:07.950 --> 05:08.850
"Sometimes"?

05:11.160 --> 05:12.060
Shut up.

05:16.000 --> 05:17.050
The Never-Ending Curse

05:19.250 --> 05:20.320
is the Formless Moon's

05:20.320 --> 05:22.360
cruelest form of punishment.

05:24.250 --> 05:26.430
People often compare moonlight to things such as water,

05:27.000 --> 05:28.100
frost,

05:29.290 --> 05:30.270
and mist.

05:31.540 --> 05:33.200
And the members of the Formless Moon

05:33.450 --> 05:34.310
take surnames like Wu,
[*mist]

05:35.000 --> 05:35.520
Lu,
[*dew]

05:36.290 --> 05:36.850
Xue,
[*snow]

05:37.500 --> 05:38.230
Shuang,
[*frost]

05:39.120 --> 05:39.680
and Bing
[*ice]

05:41.290 --> 05:43.390
as they move through the mortal world.

05:44.330 --> 05:46.310
Once we violate the sect's laws,

05:46.700 --> 05:47.430
the moonlight

05:47.540 --> 05:49.430
transforms into our surname

05:51.620 --> 05:53.310
and hunts us for eternity.

05:55.500 --> 05:57.480
The Never-Ending Curse can reach

05:58.330 --> 05:59.980
wherever the moonlight can,

06:01.080 --> 06:02.430
and it won't stop until we're dead.

06:03.670 --> 06:04.770
Xiaowei's surname

06:05.080 --> 06:05.810
is Bing,
[*ice]

06:06.500 --> 06:07.310
so

06:07.950 --> 06:09.930
what pursues her is the Ice Curse.

06:10.870 --> 06:12.100
Once it catches up to her,

06:12.500 --> 06:13.870
she'll be turned into ice

06:14.450 --> 06:15.820
and shattered into pieces.

06:18.620 --> 06:19.430
What's your surname?

06:22.450 --> 06:22.930
Lu,

06:23.790 --> 06:24.810
as in dew.

06:26.790 --> 06:28.050
My name

06:29.000 --> 06:30.100
is Lu Wuyi.

06:32.040 --> 06:32.680
That's a beautiful name.

06:35.120 --> 06:35.890
I'll remember it.

06:42.790 --> 06:44.560
As long as Xiaowei doesn't use demon magic,

06:45.000 --> 06:46.890
the Ice Curse won't lock onto her.

06:47.500 --> 06:49.020
But there is one exception.

06:53.150 --> 06:54.430
Around the full moon,

06:55.120 --> 06:56.270
the moonlight is strongest,

06:56.550 --> 06:57.560
and so is its power.

06:58.140 --> 07:00.030
Even if Xiaowei doesn't use demon magic,

07:00.330 --> 07:01.860
the Never-Ending Curse will still sense her.

07:02.580 --> 07:03.430
That means

07:04.040 --> 07:05.810
she'll have to hide in dark places

07:06.290 --> 07:07.390
to avoid the moonlight.

07:09.830 --> 07:10.810
Yesterday was the fifteenth.

07:11.580 --> 07:12.680
Today is the sixteenth.

07:13.580 --> 07:14.480
That means...

07:14.910 --> 07:17.230
The moon is the fullest on the sixteenth night of the month.

07:18.290 --> 07:19.640
Wangyan and I hurried back

07:21.080 --> 07:22.330
to enjoy

07:22.330 --> 07:23.490
tonight's moonlight.

07:25.040 --> 07:25.930
I imagine

07:27.540 --> 07:28.850
it'll be beautiful.

07:55.620 --> 07:56.890
You stayed behind,

07:57.750 --> 07:58.850
but you're not saying anything.

07:59.830 --> 08:00.730
What's on your mind?

08:01.580 --> 08:02.560
I'm thinking about you...

08:03.410 --> 08:04.770
You're thinking about me?

08:06.620 --> 08:08.270
I'm thinking about how you had the audacity to come back.

08:09.370 --> 08:11.140
- And what if I hadn't come back? - If you hadn't,

08:12.080 --> 08:13.410
I would've dragged you back myself.

08:13.500 --> 08:15.310
Then you'd better keep a close eye on me.

08:15.790 --> 08:17.030
Once I'm gone,

08:17.250 --> 08:18.410
I won't be easy to find.

08:19.700 --> 08:20.740
How about I tie you up?

08:21.580 --> 08:22.550
Want to try

08:22.750 --> 08:23.810
the Demon-Binding Rope again?

08:36.870 --> 08:38.060
What's that on your arm?

08:38.790 --> 08:40.390
A mark from the Formless Moon.

08:42.160 --> 08:42.930
Is it a moon phase?

08:45.500 --> 08:48.060
It looks like the full moon.

08:48.790 --> 08:50.430
But I prefer to call it Wangyue.
[*another term for the full moon]

08:53.620 --> 08:54.520
Wang, as in hope?

08:56.870 --> 08:58.640
As in gazing until your eyes go dry.

09:04.330 --> 09:05.650
Do all the sect members have one?

09:05.950 --> 09:07.240
Everyone except Wuyi

09:07.410 --> 09:08.350
has one.

09:09.950 --> 09:10.910
This mark

09:11.200 --> 09:13.220
will be with us for life after life.

09:30.740 --> 09:31.410
Here.

09:45.950 --> 09:46.680
I've heard

09:47.580 --> 09:49.140
that everyone in the Formless Moon

09:49.290 --> 09:50.770
has a mark on their arm.

09:51.950 --> 09:53.100
Why don't you have one?

09:56.700 --> 09:57.890
Because my moon phase

09:59.120 --> 09:59.770
is Hui.
[*new moon]

10:00.870 --> 10:01.430
Hui?

10:03.660 --> 10:04.730
I've read

10:05.330 --> 10:07.020
that the Formless Moon has seven moon phases:

10:07.500 --> 10:08.060
waning gibbous,

10:08.500 --> 10:09.060
full,

10:09.450 --> 10:10.140
last-quarter,

10:10.620 --> 10:13.770
waning crescent, waxing crescent, first-quarter, and waxing gibbous.

10:14.700 --> 10:16.180
I've never heard of Hui as a moon phase.

10:20.450 --> 10:22.770
When you can't see the moon at night,

10:23.790 --> 10:25.020
that moon phase

10:25.910 --> 10:26.640
is Hui.

10:28.450 --> 10:29.640
That's why I don't have a mark.

10:31.580 --> 10:32.770
Hui, as in regret?

10:35.120 --> 10:36.390
Hui, as in obscure and hard to understand.

10:38.580 --> 10:40.290
But it doesn't matter if I'm hard to understand.

10:41.660 --> 10:42.640
There's one person

10:44.330 --> 10:45.100
who understands me.

10:49.790 --> 10:52.390
Actually, I don't really understand you.

10:55.700 --> 10:57.020
I mean my sister, Wangyan.

10:58.830 --> 10:59.350
She knew

10:59.370 --> 11:00.940
I didn't have a moon phase on my arm,

11:01.410 --> 11:02.060
so she said

11:02.580 --> 11:03.890
she'd give me one.

11:05.500 --> 11:07.230
This hollow jade jue
[*jue: slit disc]

11:07.950 --> 11:09.180
is like the new moon.

11:10.910 --> 11:11.680
So Xiaowei

11:13.000 --> 11:13.730
has a moon phase too?

11:14.660 --> 11:16.100
Of course she does.

11:17.660 --> 11:19.480
Back then, to make sure she could find her savior,

11:20.410 --> 11:21.480
she branded him

11:21.620 --> 11:23.990
with the same mark she bore herself.

11:24.540 --> 11:26.820
That way, even through life and death,

11:26.870 --> 11:28.020
even if he vanished into the crowd

11:28.540 --> 11:29.770
and his appearance changed,

11:30.000 --> 11:31.640
she could still find him

11:31.640 --> 11:32.390
through that mark.

11:33.040 --> 11:35.180
Do you remember what you have to do

11:35.620 --> 11:36.730
to ask Lady Wei for a love talisman?

11:40.000 --> 11:40.930
Take off your clothes

11:41.750 --> 11:42.730
and bare yourself completely.

11:47.660 --> 11:48.310
So,

11:49.290 --> 11:50.560
that's to look for the mark?

11:51.080 --> 11:52.850
You catch on quick, Shiguang.

11:55.620 --> 11:56.890
Then what is Xiaowei's moon phase?

11:57.450 --> 11:57.980
Kui,
[*waning gibbous]

12:00.500 --> 12:01.560
as in indebted.

12:02.830 --> 12:03.480
The waning gibbous moon?

12:06.830 --> 12:08.180
I think I've seen it somewhere before.

12:45.120 --> 12:46.100
I'm looking at the flowers.

12:47.540 --> 12:48.560
What are you looking at?

12:52.500 --> 12:54.740
I've noticed several times before

12:54.740 --> 12:56.280
that you often stare at flowers in a daze.

12:57.120 --> 12:58.680
Do you like flowers a lot?

13:00.160 --> 13:01.480
Do you like flowers a lot?

13:07.040 --> 13:09.020
They all like gold, silver,

13:09.500 --> 13:10.480
fine silk, and satin.

13:11.910 --> 13:12.730
But I

13:15.750 --> 13:17.020
only like flowers.

13:17.910 --> 13:20.020
But no matter how beautiful a flower is, it'll still wither.

13:21.330 --> 13:22.060
It can't last forever.

13:23.580 --> 13:25.110
And that's exactly why

13:26.120 --> 13:26.980
it's more beautiful

13:28.660 --> 13:29.680
and more precious.

13:32.250 --> 13:32.980
Don't you think so?

13:35.030 --> 13:35.740
Miss Lu,

13:37.710 --> 13:38.890
have we really never met?

13:40.750 --> 13:41.650
Should we

13:43.240 --> 13:44.220
have met?

13:48.540 --> 13:49.310
Your hand is dirty.

13:49.500 --> 13:50.350
Let me wipe it for you.

14:23.750 --> 14:24.350
Miss Lu,

14:25.200 --> 14:26.270
let me ask you one more time.

14:27.910 --> 14:28.850
Before we came here,

14:29.910 --> 14:30.890
did we ever meet?

14:33.870 --> 14:34.810
I don't remember.

14:36.000 --> 14:36.680
Miss Lu,

14:37.580 --> 14:38.520
your heart is racing.

14:39.290 --> 14:40.850
Are you lying?

14:44.040 --> 14:45.100
If I'm the one lying,

14:47.500 --> 14:48.600
why are you blushing?

14:49.950 --> 14:50.430
So...

14:51.330 --> 14:52.600
so are you admitting it?

14:54.290 --> 14:55.350
Back then,

14:55.700 --> 14:57.390
you had this rag doll with you too.

14:58.750 --> 14:59.770
There aren't many grown men

15:00.290 --> 15:01.930
who still play with dolls.

15:02.830 --> 15:03.980
You were too memorable

15:04.540 --> 15:05.270
to forget.

15:07.080 --> 15:07.810
It's no

15:07.950 --> 15:08.810
ordinary doll.

15:11.080 --> 15:12.480
It's been my loyal companion

15:13.370 --> 15:14.770
since childhood.

15:16.160 --> 15:17.230
So you do remember me.

15:19.450 --> 15:20.680
But my memories of you

15:21.790 --> 15:23.020
have been blurry.

15:26.660 --> 15:27.680
Why is that?

15:28.900 --> 15:32.060
♪I raise my face, and snow veils my eyes...♪

15:33.000 --> 15:33.930
Here's a bouquet

15:34.000 --> 15:35.310
of wildflowers in bloom.

15:35.670 --> 15:36.610
Cheer up.

15:38.940 --> 15:41.700
♪Who sings this song of longing?♪

15:41.720 --> 15:42.820
Forget me.

15:42.820 --> 15:50.380
♪Ah, if it hurts, grow a flower♪

15:50.390 --> 15:51.330
Maybe

15:53.320 --> 15:54.100
you've just met

15:54.120 --> 15:55.690
too many pretty girls.

15:57.390 --> 15:59.140
Are you calling yourself pretty?

16:00.870 --> 16:01.390
You are pretty.

16:01.620 --> 16:02.230
Very pretty.

16:02.830 --> 16:03.640
You don't have to say it.

16:03.700 --> 16:04.270
I'll say it.

16:06.830 --> 16:07.600
Instead of doing your job,

16:08.290 --> 16:10.230
you're here admiring flowers and playing with the doll?

16:11.200 --> 16:12.060
You scared me!

16:13.290 --> 16:14.930
When did you get here?

16:14.930 --> 16:15.770
How much did you hear?

16:18.330 --> 16:20.020
Isn't the real business supposed to wait until tonight?

16:22.200 --> 16:22.770
By the way,

16:24.160 --> 16:25.380
there is something

16:25.450 --> 16:26.710
I really need your help with, Ji.

16:27.700 --> 16:28.430
Tell me.

16:30.120 --> 16:31.490
This is the note Xiaowei used to lure me

16:31.870 --> 16:33.410
to the workshop and frame me.

16:34.420 --> 16:35.360
[Come to the weaving workshop this afternoon.]

16:35.390 --> 16:36.220
[The deadlock can be broken. - Xiaowei]

16:37.710 --> 16:38.500
That's outrageous.

16:41.290 --> 16:42.740
Investigate the handwriting on this note

16:42.830 --> 16:43.680
and see if it gives us any clues.

16:50.830 --> 16:51.770
You really know how to order people around.

16:52.000 --> 16:52.730
Just go already.

16:58.910 --> 17:00.020
That's just how he is.

17:16.460 --> 17:17.750
If the moon

17:17.750 --> 17:19.370
doesn't come out all night,

17:20.120 --> 17:21.300
won't our plan

17:21.500 --> 17:23.180
fail?

17:32.040 --> 17:32.900
What...

17:33.080 --> 17:34.270
what are you doing?

17:35.120 --> 17:35.880
Master Wei's body

17:35.880 --> 17:37.320
should be placed in the ancestral hall,

17:37.370 --> 17:39.140
then buried and laid to rest after the funeral.

17:39.750 --> 17:41.060
What exactly are you trying to do here?

17:42.120 --> 17:43.230
Everyone, stay calm.

17:43.790 --> 17:44.730
Master Wei was killed

17:45.290 --> 17:46.270
by a demon.

17:46.830 --> 17:48.060
His spirit can only rest

17:48.290 --> 17:49.350
after the evil influence is purged.

17:50.040 --> 17:50.930
Before dawn,

17:52.200 --> 17:53.810
everyone must remain in the courtyard

17:54.700 --> 17:55.600
and help purify and guide

17:56.370 --> 17:57.430
Master Wei's soul.

18:03.410 --> 18:04.100
Purifying the soul.

18:33.910 --> 18:34.600
Guiding it onward.

18:54.310 --> 18:56.360
All of you were close to Master Wei.

18:56.870 --> 18:58.100
You must remain in the courtyard

18:58.500 --> 18:59.470
until dawn.

18:59.760 --> 19:01.000
Then the ritual will be complete.

19:02.620 --> 19:03.560
Don't worry.

19:05.120 --> 19:06.870
I'll stay by your side here.

19:08.040 --> 19:09.020
You won't be in danger.

19:18.950 --> 19:20.680
They should've started by now, right?

19:21.450 --> 19:22.930
A night hunt for Xiaowei...

19:24.000 --> 19:25.180
Wangyan, that's really brilliant.

19:26.620 --> 19:27.390
But

19:27.830 --> 19:29.180
can they really handle it?

19:31.080 --> 19:32.350
Shouldn't we go take a look?

19:32.910 --> 19:34.310
Are you worried about them

19:34.950 --> 19:35.850
or just

19:36.500 --> 19:38.230
bored staying here?

19:41.000 --> 19:42.390
You saw right through me again.

19:43.500 --> 19:44.480
Not fun at all.

19:47.700 --> 19:49.770
We've already exposed our identities.

19:50.500 --> 19:51.690
We can't let Xiaowei find out

19:51.690 --> 19:52.820
we've come back.

19:53.750 --> 19:54.600
Just stay put.

19:55.500 --> 19:56.100
Don't forget

19:56.780 --> 19:58.120
that we're waiting here

19:58.750 --> 20:00.510
because there's something else we need to do.

20:01.770 --> 20:02.810
All right,

20:03.450 --> 20:04.310
I'll do as you say, Wangyan.

20:12.620 --> 20:13.310
I need to relieve myself.

20:13.790 --> 20:14.480
Can't you wait?

20:14.790 --> 20:15.520
I'll go with you.

20:16.290 --> 20:17.140
Xiaowei still hasn't been caught.

20:18.080 --> 20:18.980
If you go alone,

20:19.500 --> 20:20.270
it could be dangerous.

20:20.700 --> 20:21.930
I'm the descendant of a military commander.

20:22.540 --> 20:23.980
Why would I fear some seductive fox demon?

20:24.500 --> 20:25.700
You stay here and mind things.

20:26.290 --> 20:27.950
A grown man following me to the latrine?

20:28.290 --> 20:29.270
Ridiculous.

20:30.040 --> 20:31.430
He should go with you.

20:32.290 --> 20:32.980
Otherwise,

20:34.160 --> 20:35.350
we would be worried.

20:50.540 --> 20:51.730
Ms. Yu, where are you going?

20:54.120 --> 20:54.810
The wind is strong tonight.

20:55.620 --> 20:56.890
I'm going back to my room to get a cloak.

20:59.000 --> 20:59.600
All right.

21:08.910 --> 21:09.930
On a starless, moonless night like this,

21:10.620 --> 21:12.180
what are you looking at, Steward Luo?

21:13.910 --> 21:14.890
With no stars and no moon,

21:16.500 --> 21:17.520
and night at its darkest,

21:18.950 --> 21:20.180
I'm just a little afraid.

21:43.870 --> 21:45.730
Mr. Liu, you've been looking up nonstop.

21:46.790 --> 21:48.810
What exactly are you looking at?

21:50.330 --> 21:51.680
I wanted to admire the moon.

21:53.490 --> 21:54.350
Too bad

21:55.250 --> 21:56.780
these tactless clouds

21:57.670 --> 21:59.130
have hidden away

22:00.040 --> 22:01.150
all that beautiful moonlight.

22:02.540 --> 22:04.480
So you enjoy moon-watching, Mr. Liu?

22:05.660 --> 22:06.600
Then how come

22:07.230 --> 22:08.930
you stay in your room

22:09.500 --> 22:11.060
and never go out most nights?

22:12.910 --> 22:13.960
I go to bed early.

22:17.700 --> 22:19.060
The moonlight is dim tonight,

22:20.160 --> 22:21.390
and it's hard to see clearly.

22:22.290 --> 22:23.020
I'd better

22:23.040 --> 22:24.180
lead the way for you

22:24.790 --> 22:26.100
so we can head back sooner.

22:56.750 --> 22:58.480
I just slipped and fell.

22:59.700 --> 23:01.310
If you won't help me up, fine.

23:01.830 --> 23:02.910
But why do you look

23:02.910 --> 23:04.070
like you want to eat me alive?

23:15.160 --> 23:16.680
Ever since Wei Qing passed,

23:18.000 --> 23:19.850
the Wei household has fallen apart.

23:20.910 --> 23:22.060
The servants have all

23:22.500 --> 23:23.230
grown lazy.

23:24.080 --> 23:26.270
They won't even clean up the standing water in the corridor now.

24:02.160 --> 24:03.180
The ritual isn't over yet.

24:04.040 --> 24:05.310
Where are you going, Steward Luo?

24:06.080 --> 24:07.140
To the dye workshop.

24:07.910 --> 24:09.180
In the middle of the night?

24:09.750 --> 24:10.850
You may not know this, Master Wu,

24:11.450 --> 24:13.140
but dye-making is a complicated process.

24:13.620 --> 24:15.060
How long the materials need to soak

24:15.200 --> 24:16.810
depends on the weather and temperature.

24:17.080 --> 24:18.060
They have to be checked constantly.

24:19.120 --> 24:19.850
Master Wei

24:20.410 --> 24:21.600
may be gone,

24:22.370 --> 24:23.560
but the Wei family's business

24:24.450 --> 24:25.600
still has to go on, doesn't it?

24:27.450 --> 24:28.750
In a household this large,

24:29.410 --> 24:30.270
do you really need

24:30.500 --> 24:31.730
to handle such minor matters yourself?

24:33.660 --> 24:35.480
Too many tragedies have struck the household lately.

24:36.790 --> 24:38.640
The servants are already demoralized.

24:39.160 --> 24:40.060
Business comes first.

24:40.790 --> 24:42.100
Let Steward Luo go.

24:50.750 --> 24:51.430
I'll go with you.

24:55.450 --> 24:56.100
Steward Luo.

25:03.370 --> 25:04.020
Thank you for your hard work.

25:04.620 --> 25:05.430
It's cold at night.

25:05.700 --> 25:06.480
Keep yourself warm.

25:11.450 --> 25:12.180
Thank you.

25:26.870 --> 25:27.560
Where's Ms. Yu?

25:28.620 --> 25:30.020
She went back to her room to get a cloak.

25:33.080 --> 25:33.770
I'll go check on her.

25:49.500 --> 25:50.640
The servants have all

25:51.090 --> 25:52.010
grown lazy.

25:52.750 --> 25:53.980
They won't even clean up the standing water

25:54.000 --> 25:54.960
in the corridor now.

25:57.790 --> 25:58.430
Just as I thought.

26:00.040 --> 26:01.390
Fox demons really do love to lie.

26:06.830 --> 26:07.430
Not good.

26:08.660 --> 26:09.480
Only Ji Ling is with him.

26:13.290 --> 26:14.480
You gave her your outer robe.

26:15.120 --> 26:15.850
Aren't you cold?

26:18.290 --> 26:18.980
When the heart is warm,

26:19.580 --> 26:20.310
the body doesn't feel cold.

26:21.540 --> 26:22.600
Do you really have one?

26:24.870 --> 26:25.640
Have what?

26:26.830 --> 26:27.560
A heart.

26:31.160 --> 26:32.520
If you really like her,

26:33.200 --> 26:34.390
you can't just do little things

26:34.450 --> 26:35.890
like bringing her tea and water.

26:36.700 --> 26:37.810
That won't move her.

26:39.950 --> 26:41.480
If you have something to say, just say it.

26:41.950 --> 26:42.890
I'm a warrior.

26:43.160 --> 26:43.850
I like things direct.

26:44.830 --> 26:46.390
I can't stand people

26:46.950 --> 26:47.930
beating around the bush.

26:49.000 --> 26:49.980
It gives me a headache.

26:51.580 --> 26:53.020
If you like her that much,

26:53.750 --> 26:55.480
why not just go to Weimiao Pavilion

26:55.790 --> 26:56.730
and ask for a talisman?

27:01.830 --> 27:03.430
Can love won through a talisman

27:04.870 --> 27:05.970
really be called love?

27:06.620 --> 27:07.990
It'll be nothing but an illusion.

27:08.910 --> 27:10.600
You're a clever man, Master Ji Ling.

27:11.250 --> 27:12.430
Surely you can see that too.

27:13.750 --> 27:15.600
Since you know that love forced by a talisman

27:15.660 --> 27:16.560
is false,

27:17.950 --> 27:18.730
why do you think

27:19.750 --> 27:21.100
the head of Weimiao Pavilion

27:22.700 --> 27:24.430
goes to such lengths

27:24.500 --> 27:25.730
to do all this?

27:26.790 --> 27:28.730
Then you'd have to ask her.

27:32.370 --> 27:33.270
I am asking.

27:40.500 --> 27:41.600
Why are you so nervous?

27:42.580 --> 27:43.270
Are you

27:43.660 --> 27:45.270
the head of Weimiao Pavilion?

27:51.370 --> 27:52.520
Are you Xiaowei?

28:02.620 --> 28:03.680
They all say Steward Luo

28:04.060 --> 28:06.100
is indispensable to the Wei household.

28:06.600 --> 28:08.160
You handle everything yourself,

28:08.700 --> 28:09.540
even the account books,

28:10.160 --> 28:12.370
recording every detail personally.

28:13.370 --> 28:14.480
I'm the steward.

28:14.750 --> 28:15.980
It's only right that I keep the books myself.

28:16.750 --> 28:18.060
What are you implying, Master Li?

28:22.250 --> 28:23.430
I have a note here.

28:28.620 --> 28:29.680
The handwriting on it

28:30.290 --> 28:31.980
matches the writing in your account books

28:32.000 --> 28:32.910
exactly.

28:33.790 --> 28:34.850
I'd like you to take a look.

28:51.160 --> 28:52.350
I've never seen this note before.

28:53.290 --> 28:54.100
I went to the fabric house

28:54.830 --> 28:56.230
and compared it with your ledger.

28:57.450 --> 28:59.170
It is your handwriting.

28:59.700 --> 29:01.050
What you may not know, Master Li,

29:02.000 --> 29:04.160
is that while I know a bit about weaving and tailoring,

29:04.700 --> 29:05.810
I've never had any schooling.

29:06.750 --> 29:07.770
Master Wei was kind enough

29:08.290 --> 29:09.680
to teach me to read and write.

29:10.290 --> 29:11.430
He even gave me copybooks in his own hand

29:11.450 --> 29:12.680
for me to practice from.

29:13.660 --> 29:14.730
So strictly speaking,

29:16.120 --> 29:17.640
the handwriting on this note

29:18.410 --> 29:20.020
looks more like Master Wei's.

29:22.370 --> 29:23.180
The servants said

29:24.250 --> 29:25.430
you were the last person

29:27.410 --> 29:28.350
to enter his room

29:28.410 --> 29:29.560
before Master Wei died.

29:31.830 --> 29:32.730
That's not true.

29:34.000 --> 29:35.140
They were mistaken.

29:39.500 --> 29:40.390
The fox demon...

29:41.330 --> 29:42.310
It's the fox demon!

30:00.120 --> 30:01.430
Why isn't she out yet?

30:06.020 --> 30:08.740
[Golden Weave]

30:38.910 --> 30:39.600
Wuyi!

30:51.790 --> 30:52.680
Master Wu,

30:54.120 --> 30:55.060
what are you doing?

30:55.830 --> 30:56.980
And what are you doing?

30:58.950 --> 30:59.680
I've been kneeling so long

31:00.500 --> 31:01.180
my legs went numb.

31:02.080 --> 31:03.560
I just wanted to get up and stretch.

31:04.370 --> 31:05.140
Still acting?

31:06.540 --> 31:07.440
Admit it. You are...

31:07.620 --> 31:09.060
Ms. Yu has been attacked by the fox demon.

31:24.660 --> 31:25.980
Are you really not...?

31:30.040 --> 31:30.890
Did we get it wrong?

31:31.620 --> 31:32.060
The demon...

31:32.450 --> 31:33.100
The fox demon...

31:33.790 --> 31:35.020
The fox demon is in the dye workshop!

31:36.450 --> 31:38.230
Li Jie is fighting it!

31:40.910 --> 31:41.770
Li Jie...

32:07.950 --> 32:09.270
Li Jie, is there really a fox demon?

32:09.660 --> 32:10.180
There was,

32:10.790 --> 32:11.930
but then it suddenly disappeared.

32:12.790 --> 32:13.680
How is that possible?

32:31.910 --> 32:32.480
Wangyan,

32:33.580 --> 32:34.600
the moon is out.

33:28.080 --> 33:28.730
Break!

33:40.790 --> 33:42.390
If you don't want the Ice Curse to consume you,

33:42.830 --> 33:44.140
stop using demon magic.

33:45.120 --> 33:46.140
Show your true form,

33:47.290 --> 33:48.310
Liu Weixue.

34:01.160 --> 34:02.230
So it really is Liu Weixue.

34:03.660 --> 34:05.310
But I was with him the whole time just now.

34:05.870 --> 34:07.730
Did he use Word Magic on me?

34:10.370 --> 34:11.810
He wouldn't dare.

34:12.440 --> 34:13.360
Otherwise,

34:14.040 --> 34:15.570
the Ice Curse would've come long ago.

34:16.250 --> 34:17.180
Then why did he

34:17.200 --> 34:18.270
suddenly use demon magic

34:18.290 --> 34:19.230
and reveal his demon form?

34:19.830 --> 34:20.520
Xiaowei,

34:22.700 --> 34:23.730
it's been a while.

34:28.040 --> 34:28.770
How...

34:30.200 --> 34:31.830
how did you figure me out?

34:32.580 --> 34:34.100
We went down the wrong path at first

34:34.950 --> 34:36.350
and thought Xiaowei was a woman.

34:37.290 --> 34:37.930
Otherwise,

34:39.080 --> 34:40.180
we would've caught you long ago.

34:41.040 --> 34:41.810
Xiaowei,

34:42.290 --> 34:44.310
you'd hidden yourself well all along.

34:44.950 --> 34:46.230
But on the wedding night,

34:46.700 --> 34:48.020
you couldn't resist using demon magic,

34:48.580 --> 34:50.680
and that drew the Ice Curse.

35:15.500 --> 35:16.180
Vile demon!

35:28.580 --> 35:29.140
That night,

35:29.830 --> 35:31.100
all of us saw

35:31.660 --> 35:33.480
Xiaowei being chased by the Ice Curse,

35:34.160 --> 35:35.140
and its back foot got frostbitten.

35:38.500 --> 35:38.930
It hurts.

35:39.140 --> 35:40.170
- You were clever. - It hurts.

35:40.750 --> 35:42.810
Feigning drunkenness, you pretended to twist your ankle

35:43.120 --> 35:44.600
to cover up the injury

35:44.600 --> 35:45.640
caused by the Ice Curse.

35:46.410 --> 35:47.640
An ordinary sprain

35:47.660 --> 35:48.480
heals in a few days.

35:49.410 --> 35:50.480
But frostbite from that curse

35:51.160 --> 35:52.230
is much harder to recover from.

35:52.830 --> 35:54.100
Just now, when I went with you to the latrine,

35:54.870 --> 35:56.480
I noticed you were still having trouble walking.

35:59.000 --> 36:00.230
You saw I was getting suspicious,

36:01.160 --> 36:02.980
so you lied and said there was standing water on the ground

36:03.500 --> 36:04.180
and that you'd slipped.

36:04.700 --> 36:05.480
That's not

36:05.700 --> 36:07.060
the only way you gave yourself away.

36:07.660 --> 36:09.100
Demons can wear countless human guises,

36:09.540 --> 36:10.600
but their demonic nature

36:11.080 --> 36:12.100
is hard to change.

36:12.870 --> 36:15.020
Habits and preferences formed over hundreds of years

36:15.280 --> 36:16.500
certainly can't be

36:17.250 --> 36:18.350
changed overnight.

36:18.370 --> 36:19.930
Young Master Liu has lived in comfort since childhood.

36:20.500 --> 36:22.480
He only sleeps on tussah silk bedding.

36:23.160 --> 36:24.230
A martial artist

36:24.620 --> 36:26.980
can sleep rough and eat rough.

36:27.620 --> 36:28.480
No way someone like that

36:28.700 --> 36:30.560
would sleep only on tussah silk.

36:31.000 --> 36:32.480
Lady Wei really lives in luxury.

36:32.870 --> 36:34.560
All her bedding is made of tussah silk.

36:38.120 --> 36:39.420
So comfortable.

36:41.370 --> 36:42.730
Xiaowei severed the spiritual tail long ago

36:43.120 --> 36:44.430
and lost the sense of smell.

36:45.040 --> 36:46.270
You can smell that from that far away?

37:01.120 --> 37:02.140
What about now?

37:03.910 --> 37:04.930
Go wash up.

37:08.790 --> 37:09.640
I see.

37:10.870 --> 37:12.060
I'll go bathe right now.

37:12.700 --> 37:13.980
What Ms. Yu smelled

37:14.200 --> 37:15.810
was actually the scent of the weasel demon

37:16.040 --> 37:17.180
inside Wu Shiguang's Cosmic Pouch.

37:17.790 --> 37:19.340
After Li Jie took the pouch away,

37:19.620 --> 37:21.390
Wu Shiguang no longer smelled of it.

37:21.910 --> 37:23.560
But you still pretended you could smell it

37:23.570 --> 37:24.680
and kept lying

37:24.910 --> 37:27.020
to hide the fact that you'd lost your sense of smell.

37:27.950 --> 37:28.560
Xiaowei,

37:29.660 --> 37:31.430
are you still going to deny it?

37:46.200 --> 37:46.930
Shengwei?

37:47.950 --> 37:48.770
How did this happen?

37:50.040 --> 37:50.600
Shengwei.

37:50.840 --> 37:51.860
Shengwei!

37:52.830 --> 37:53.590
Shengwei...

37:54.250 --> 37:55.350
You clearly killed her

37:55.370 --> 37:56.230
by ripping out her heart.

37:57.080 --> 37:57.970
Drop the act.

37:58.500 --> 37:59.490
That's not true.

37:59.700 --> 38:00.710
That's not true.

38:01.410 --> 38:02.200
Shengwei.

38:02.830 --> 38:03.480
Shengwei.

38:03.500 --> 38:04.480
Wake up, Shengwei!

38:05.080 --> 38:05.680
Shengwei!

38:06.290 --> 38:06.770
Shengwei...

38:07.120 --> 38:08.480
I didn't do it. Untie me!

38:08.660 --> 38:09.430
Shengwei!

38:10.580 --> 38:11.680
Untie me!

38:41.660 --> 38:42.770
She's still alive.

38:44.330 --> 38:45.890
But her heart is badly damaged,

38:45.890 --> 38:46.860
and she's lost too much blood.

38:47.620 --> 38:49.810
My seal will only slow the bleeding for a short while.

38:50.450 --> 38:51.780
It can't save her.

38:52.580 --> 38:54.950
It can only buy her a little more time.

38:55.540 --> 38:57.240
I saw the wound on the left side of her chest

38:57.330 --> 38:59.070
and thought she'd stopped breathing, so I didn't stay.

38:59.440 --> 39:00.390
How is she

39:01.080 --> 39:02.480
still alive now?

39:04.540 --> 39:05.480
You did it.

39:06.750 --> 39:08.060
You killed her.

39:09.500 --> 39:10.140
Fox demon,

39:10.540 --> 39:11.600
I'll kill you!

39:25.430 --> 39:26.620
I wanted to repay her.

39:28.670 --> 39:30.660
How could I ever hurt her?

39:34.670 --> 39:35.330
She's the Wang Sheng

39:35.400 --> 39:37.510
I've searched for across lifetimes.

40:21.290 --> 40:23.060
A packed bundle.

40:27.370 --> 40:28.020
Chestnut cakes.

40:30.790 --> 40:31.770
A shadow puppet.

41:11.350 --> 41:13.420
So as it turned out,

41:14.270 --> 41:15.730
Ms. Yu was Wang Sheng.

41:16.880 --> 41:17.840
But then why

41:18.160 --> 41:19.690
is there a waning moon mark

41:20.140 --> 41:22.020
on Wei Qing's sole?

41:22.950 --> 41:24.180
That's only an old scar.

41:37.620 --> 41:39.310
Scars can be erased with magic.

41:40.500 --> 41:41.930
But a Formless Moon mark

41:42.950 --> 41:44.140
can never be removed.

41:44.540 --> 41:45.520
It remains lifetime after lifetime.

41:48.870 --> 41:49.890
You discovered it when you

41:49.910 --> 41:51.020
attacked Ms. Yu half a month ago,

41:51.040 --> 41:51.730
didn't you?

42:02.830 --> 42:03.480
But

42:04.790 --> 42:05.850
it was already too late.

42:17.290 --> 42:19.020
I had already granted a love talisman to Wei Qing.

42:20.410 --> 42:21.140
I never imagined

42:22.120 --> 42:23.630
that by doing so, I'd be signing a death warrant

42:23.630 --> 42:25.030
for the one I'd been searching for.

42:31.160 --> 42:32.850
I couldn't let Shengwei die,

42:33.490 --> 42:34.350
so I

42:35.330 --> 42:36.430
came to the Wei mansion.

42:37.500 --> 42:38.610
I needed to make sure she'd never

42:38.610 --> 42:39.960
suffer the blowback of the Fox-Allure Spell.

42:41.120 --> 42:41.770
Unfortunately,

42:42.450 --> 42:43.920
that's

42:44.160 --> 42:45.100
impossible.

42:45.720 --> 42:47.250
As long as the love remains,

42:48.190 --> 42:49.500
the spell can't be lifted.

42:50.230 --> 42:51.130
Even killing someone

42:51.620 --> 42:52.430
won't end it.

42:53.250 --> 42:54.020
No, it can be lifted

42:55.370 --> 42:56.600
once the one who asked for the talisman

42:58.200 --> 42:59.270
falls for someone else.

43:00.160 --> 43:00.980
I see.

43:02.620 --> 43:03.930
You used another love talisman

43:04.500 --> 43:06.390
to make Wei Qing fall for someone else.

43:07.330 --> 43:08.680
And the perfect choice happened to be

43:09.040 --> 43:10.770
right in front of you:

43:12.330 --> 43:13.060
Luo Wei.

43:15.820 --> 43:18.660
[Yu Shengwei is my closest and dearest friend. - Luo Wei]

43:18.660 --> 43:19.430
Yu Shengwei

43:20.040 --> 43:22.020
is my closest and dearest friend.

43:22.370 --> 43:23.180
You knew

43:23.540 --> 43:24.680
that she and Ms. Yu

43:25.040 --> 43:25.810
were intimate friends.

43:26.160 --> 43:26.890
Without Ms. Yu,

43:27.250 --> 43:28.270
she could never have worked here.

43:31.120 --> 43:32.740
Luo Wei tried to break the two of them apart

43:33.200 --> 43:34.230
not because of Master Wei,

43:35.330 --> 43:36.430
but because of Ms. Yu.

43:38.040 --> 43:39.830
Everyone says Weimiao Pavilion is the best place

43:39.830 --> 43:40.780
to pray for love.

43:41.450 --> 43:42.890
If I went to ask for a talisman,

43:43.660 --> 43:44.520
would your heart...

43:46.950 --> 43:48.310
would your heart

43:48.330 --> 43:49.350
finally be mine?

43:53.620 --> 43:54.890
You secretly nudged Luo Wei

43:55.080 --> 43:56.020
into seeking a love talisman.

43:57.580 --> 43:58.480
And so Master Wei

43:59.160 --> 44:00.230
fell for Luo Wei.

44:00.950 --> 44:01.640
After that,

44:02.160 --> 44:03.230
his feelings for Yu Shengwei

44:03.540 --> 44:04.480
naturally disappeared.

44:05.540 --> 44:07.730
Thus, the Fox-Allure Spell on her was lifted.

44:13.750 --> 44:15.630
But why did you still want Wei Qing dead

44:16.290 --> 44:17.650
after the spell had been lifted?

44:18.580 --> 44:21.060
Because he refused to divorce Shengwei.

44:21.700 --> 44:22.890
He wouldn't set her free.

44:23.500 --> 44:24.480
He deserved to die.

44:26.290 --> 44:27.140
You actually used

44:27.200 --> 44:28.600
the blowback of the Fox-Allure Spell to kill.

44:29.290 --> 44:30.640
So it was you who switched the talismans.

44:32.160 --> 44:32.980
It wasn't me.

44:34.660 --> 44:35.480
It was Luo Wei.

44:36.500 --> 44:37.560
She stole

44:38.040 --> 44:39.270
the love talisman before I could.

44:49.830 --> 44:50.560
Mr. Liu,

44:52.200 --> 44:53.230
are you looking for something?

44:53.500 --> 44:54.430
Why are your clothes in such a mess?

44:55.160 --> 44:55.770
Where's your belt?

44:57.620 --> 44:58.310
Steward Luo

44:58.330 --> 44:59.810
said Master Wei's belt was damaged,

45:00.290 --> 45:01.770
so she took it away to mend it for him.

45:11.450 --> 45:12.100
It's no use.

45:15.750 --> 45:16.980
But those demon hunters said...

45:17.120 --> 45:17.930
I lied to them.

45:19.080 --> 45:19.770
Only the person

45:20.410 --> 45:21.480
under the spell

45:21.500 --> 45:22.480
can tear up the talisman.

45:23.290 --> 45:24.050
No one else

45:24.250 --> 45:26.020
can destroy it.

45:26.370 --> 45:28.770
Only if Wei Qing tears it up himself

45:29.500 --> 45:30.830
will the blowback be triggered.

45:31.950 --> 45:33.430
If you really want him dead,

45:34.830 --> 45:36.390
do as I say.

45:38.250 --> 45:39.270
You have Shengwei's sachet

45:40.580 --> 45:41.730
with you too, right?

45:44.500 --> 45:46.270
If Yu Shengwei really divorces you,

45:46.950 --> 45:47.770
you will become

45:47.830 --> 45:49.140
the laughingstock of the entire Luo'an City.

45:49.950 --> 45:50.850
Then what should I do?

45:52.520 --> 45:54.080
How did you get her sachet?

45:55.190 --> 45:56.370
I had Luo Wei

45:56.640 --> 45:58.580
cover the talisman bearing her name and Wei Qing's

45:59.400 --> 46:01.490
with a thin sheet of paper

46:03.320 --> 46:05.020
bearing the names Wei Qing

46:05.660 --> 46:07.140
[Yu Shengwei]
and Yu Shengwei.

46:07.580 --> 46:08.310
Tear it up,

46:09.000 --> 46:10.230
and everything will be solved.

46:14.500 --> 46:15.480
You lied to me...

46:22.640 --> 46:23.860
Your plan worked.

46:24.230 --> 46:24.860
Wei Qing

46:25.880 --> 46:27.290
killed himself.

46:29.290 --> 46:31.230
Then who was the fox demon

46:32.160 --> 46:32.810
who attacked Ms. Yu?

46:33.500 --> 46:34.730
She wasn't attacked by a fox demon.

46:35.330 --> 46:36.040
I set up a protective barrier

46:36.040 --> 46:37.060
around the Wei mansion.

46:37.500 --> 46:38.680
If any demon had tried to cause trouble,

46:39.200 --> 46:40.310
I would've sensed it at once.

46:41.250 --> 46:42.230
A demon couldn't make a move,

46:42.620 --> 46:43.310
but a human could.

46:48.870 --> 46:49.480
Luo Wei,

46:50.370 --> 46:51.310
you're worse than a demon.

46:52.660 --> 46:54.930
One, two, three, four.

46:55.330 --> 46:56.460
These four items

46:56.660 --> 46:57.480
hold all the secrets

46:57.700 --> 46:59.000
behind tonight's

46:59.200 --> 47:00.180
murder case.

47:11.900 --> 47:13.060
♪It's your light♪

47:13.260 --> 47:15.140
♪Your storms, your watchful eyes♪

47:15.300 --> 47:18.420
♪That set the night alight♪

47:18.780 --> 47:25.300
♪And lead me through the fight♪

47:27.060 --> 47:28.940
♪Jade in the lake, sand in my hand♪

47:29.380 --> 47:33.820
♪Let bitter seeds grow, let fate bloom♪

47:34.620 --> 47:36.300
♪Face in the mirror, veiled in mist♪

47:36.460 --> 47:41.860
♪Till snow has kissed dark hair to white♪

47:42.620 --> 47:48.020
♪Night lamp burning by the old table♪

47:50.340 --> 47:56.380
♪Stitch by stitch, mending moonlight♪

47:57.340 --> 47:59.500
♪The dancing light, the shattered wave♪

47:59.780 --> 48:04.620
♪Are all my helpless, drifting haze♪

48:04.980 --> 48:07.300
♪The boiling frost, the stubborn stare♪

48:07.500 --> 48:12.580
♪Are all the pride I'll never wear♪

48:12.820 --> 48:14.820
♪Your shoulder, your tear-bright eyes♪

48:15.100 --> 48:19.460
♪Are the strength that lifts my dreams to the skies♪

48:20.460 --> 48:27.420
♪Stay with me, let's gaze above♪

48:43.980 --> 48:46.940
♪Nowhere to rest, nowhere to hide♪

48:48.020 --> 48:51.420
♪Bare in body yet boundless inside♪

48:52.220 --> 48:54.740
♪Nothing to seek, nothing to erase♪

48:54.980 --> 48:58.060
♪Like water gone, like the formless moon♪

48:58.460 --> 49:00.780
♪Let every dream and wild desire♪

49:01.300 --> 49:05.700
♪Forge the edge that lifts us higher♪

49:05.940 --> 49:08.100
♪Bells through endless time, sun and moon alike in shine♪

49:08.500 --> 49:13.460
♪Love and hate all earn their crown♪

49:13.700 --> 49:14.860
♪It's your light♪

49:15.060 --> 49:16.900
♪Your storms, your watchful eyes♪

49:17.100 --> 49:20.220
♪That set the night alight♪

49:20.980 --> 49:30.420
♪And lead me sailing afar♪
